29:07.000Z","msg":"2/3去睇神戶勝利船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到現場買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:00:29.000Z","msg":"神船唔洗旨意現場買到飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e133e1a48d3b5e44330d8a1c02047f44246623","tid":1035852,"uid":91115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c50a11fe65dd70e54cf1be04d03b2441e902eed","tid":1035852,"uid":201374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"cut晒啲二三線城市,淨係去啲有飛機到嘅大城市咁去嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣玩就預咗去到盡，夜晚先搭車轉地方用盡晒所有時間<br />\n長崎(落機)<br />\n長崎(1日) 去佐世保<br />\n佐世保(半日)  去福岡<br />\n福岡(1日) 繼續住福岡<br />\n朝早小倉 中午門司 下午唐戶(1日) 去廣島<br />\n廣島(1日) 繼續住廣島<br />\n尾道(1日) 去岡山<br />\n岡山、倉敷、吉備津(1日) 去鳥取<br />\n鳥取(1日) 去姫路<br />\n姫路(半日)、神戸(半日)  去大阪<br />\n京阪奈(3日)  去名古屋<br />\n名古屋(1日) 去東京   (名古屋就真係唔知去做乜，真係可以cut)<br />\n剩低嘅全東京<br />\n<br />\n去旅行，去到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:00:36.000Z","msg":"係咯<br />\n樓上傻的嗎?<br />\n話哂有16日, 買個全國14日夠哂玩"},{"pid":"c9b6f731433395fd26a38ea7eeb95f2e1e2029d8","tid":1035852,"uid":77723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"297ec47874f6e5514afac6c5bfd64962df9da8f0","tid":1035852,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10a7055fe727aeec13134c4b165585e51bd03db2","tid":1035852,"uid":77723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eee59ab3047f59d75a86f434fed24debed57e76","tid":1035852,"uid":131967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T21:51:29.000Z","msg":"黎緊應該會6月頭去日本，想去以下既地方:<br />\n<br />\n長崎～福岡～廣島～岡山～鳥取～神戸～大阪～京都～名古屋～東京<br />\n<br />\n但頂盡得16日時間<br />\n我知16日要去哂哩堆地方會超級趕